.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: grey, emerald, lilac, purple, turquise
Nationality: russian, polish, argentine, chinese, british
Cigar: bongani, turquisemaster, aristoff, swisher, siglo
Beverage: 7up, cola, almond-milk, hot-chocolate, sprite
Pet: bird, ferret, cat, snake, frog

1. Nationality:russian == Color:grey
2. Nationality:polish == Pet:bird
3. Beverage:7up == Color:emerald
4. Nationality:argentine == Beverage:cola
5. Color:emerald is to the right of Color:lilac
6. Cigar:bongani == Pet:frog
7. Cigar:turquisemaster == Color:purple
8. Beverage:almond-milk is in the middle
9. Nationality:chinese is on the far left
10. Cigar:aristoff is on the left or right of Pet:ferret
11. Cigar:turquisemaster is to the left or right of Pet:snake
12. Cigar:swisher == Beverage:hot-chocolate
13. Nationality:british == Cigar:siglo
14. Nationality:chinese is to the left or right of Color:turquise

.:: Answer ::.
